      <title outputclass="H4ForH3_1_9" class="- topic/title ">
         <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">42.709-4</ph> Computing
interest.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
         <p otherprops="Body"
            outputclass="Body"
            class="- topic/p "
            id="d2523e13">For <ph outputclass="ClauseProvisionXREF" class="- topic/ph ">
               <xref href="FAR-i1075370.dita#i1075370"
                     base="i1075370"
                     outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                     class="- topic/xref ">42.709-1</xref>(a)(1)</ph>(ii),
compute interest on any paid portion of the disallowed cost as follows:</p>
         <ol id="d2509e21" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li otherprops="abc" outputclass="H5_abc" class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d2523e26" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph> Consider the overpayment to have
occurred, and interest to have begun accumulating, from the midpoint
of the contractorâ€™s fiscal year. Use an alternate equitable method
if the cost was not paid evenly over the fiscal year.</p>
            </li>
            <li otherprops="abc" outputclass="H5_abc" class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d2523e35" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph> Use the interest rate specified
by the Secretary of the Treasury pursuant to Pub.L.92-41 (85 Stat.
97).</p>
            </li>
            <li otherprops="abc" outputclass="H5_abc" class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d2523e44" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph> Compute interest from the date
of overpayment to the date of the demand letter for payment of the
penalty.</p>
            </li>
            <li otherprops="abc" outputclass="H5_abc" class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d2523e53" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(d)</ph> Determine the paid portion of
the disallowed costs in consultation with the contract auditor.</p>
            </li>
         </ol>
      </conbody>
   </concept>
